text: Tukuran Technical-Vocational High School, also referred to by the acronym TTVHS, is a public high school located in Tukuran, Zamboanga del Sur, Philippines. It is composed of five campuses and the leading Public High School in the municipality. It is the Venue of SSDC meet in the cluster of Aurora, Labangan and Tukuran for the preparation for yearly provincial meet.Batikang Maninisid The Hillside Spark 2009 ==Campuses== {| class="wikitable" |- !
